title: Jake W - Mortal Kombat.mp4
description:
This is the Jake Walmsley "Syncsta" version of Mortal Kombat.  It has been downloaded from YouTube and transcoded for use with iPod video, AppleTV, and other mpeg4 playback devices.

***WARNING***:  This is a TEST version that has transcoding errors in the first three seconds.  You will notice a green background with several squares with strange shading of the image in the background.  The cause of these errors is known and will be corrected in a future version.

PLEASE COMMENT to let me know if this works with your Video iPods.
